  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>Here is an example of exporting Ri Attributes (e.g. Ri Round Curve) to an Alembic File for reading into RenderMan for Maya (RfM), which expects rman__ and not ri_ as Houdini has historically used.  </p><ul><li><p>Add an <strong>AttributeCreate</strong> node.</p></li><li><p>Name it as how it is named in RenderMan for Maya, e.g. rman__riattr__dice_roundcurve</p></li><li><p>Set the Class to <strong>Detail</strong></p></li><li><p>Set the Value expression to the Ri Attribute (e.g. ri_roundcurve)</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1141\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646645/attributecreate_roundcurve.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433156567&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=864&amp;height=432\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646645/attributecreate_roundcurve.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433156567&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"432\" data-width=\"864\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646659\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"attributecreate_roundcurve.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646645\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"4828e248-3acf-48f8-8845-c3c432da728d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646645/attributecreate_roundcurve.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433156567&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=864&amp;height=432 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646645/attributecreate_roundcurve.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433156567&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=864&amp;height=432 1x\"></span><p /><p>You can download this example here: <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19268099/curves_alembicattr.hip?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1694038254025&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" rel=\"nofollow\">curves_alembicattr.hip</a></p><p>When you read the alembic file into RfM, you will see the Round Curve attribute with the setting from Houdini.</p><p /><p />"
    }
  },
